data.description: Here is a rare opportunity to own a home within walking distance of Lake Michigan. Situated on over an acre lot, this home offers over 2500 square feet, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with one additional quarter bath, and a finished basement.  This home is just over a quarter mile away from the Dunes of Lake Michigan and Hamlin Lake which is known for its clean sandy bottom water and excellent fishing. Lincoln Hills Golf Club is a stones throw from this house, along with Stix bowling and dining that offers great food, music and fun.  Within minutes you will find yourself downtown Ludington, a charming town that sets on the shore of Lake Michigan, with so much to offer from miles of beaches,  shops, dining and more. Ludington is a destination area and this house would make a great opportunity for a rental or air bnb investment. Short term rentals are allowed upon township approval. This home has been loved by the same owners for over 30 years and is ready for someone to make it their own.
